{"tid":1655930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"13歲男生 被控4項控罪提堂","createTime":"2019-10-15T10:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T13:46:49.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"475c1acc60e75294ce895c0ed001e02fe76e3062","tid":1655930,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:18:39.000Z","msg":"上星期日的示威活動，一名身穿黑衣的便衣警於將軍澳被人毆打，隨身警棍懷疑被人扔入溝渠，防暴警察其後趕至救援。一名13歲男學生事後被控非法集結、非法禁錮他人、違反禁蒙面法及有意圖而傷人等4項控罪。案件在東區裁判法院提訊。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，13歲被告於10月13日在將軍澳唐俊街及唐德街一帶，與其他不知名人士參與非法集結、身處非法集結時使用蒙面用品，即一個耳掛式口罩、非法及惡意禁錮警員，以及意圖使警員身體受嚴重傷害。<br />\n<br />\n被告現時留院，缺席聆訊，案件押後至10月18日再訊，被告直至出院將交由警方看管。"},{"pid":"95d1990ae7a746dc3446f99ed210ddf0b9a5cdb2","tid":1655930,"uid":36035,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:19:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8223c7c20e32ec62ab10e1c15a11e9e22b1dee7","tid":1655930,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:19:45.000Z","msg":"案件押後至10月18日再訊，<span style=\"color: red;\">被告直至出院將交由警方看管。</span>"},{"pid":"52a2940973fb63a2492d3c6507b382fcce7f06e9","tid":1655930,"uid":33527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />13歲咋屌"},{"pid":"6284618eda2e387dcb26ae818b3550beb04fc362","tid":1655930,"uid":47905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:20:18.000Z","msg":"被告直至出院將交由警方看管<br />\n<br />\n又用私刑"},{"pid":"ff31ff7de8462bdf0a9927f3032bbd8d3fbb21d8","tid":1655930,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"講左幾多次 番屋企前要反跟蹤同換裝呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec782ebea4a8220fc5566c1f122a9436e5f3c74","tid":1655930,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\